Scourge of the Square~
marauders~
   Arr, even a pirate's got standards! A pack of marauders has been robbing
honest folk here in the square and givin' the rest of us a bad name. Send
three of the scurvy dogs to the depths, and I'll share me doubloons.
~
   Ha! Three fewer cutthroats in New Orleans Square. Ye've a pirate's heart,
friend. Here's yer share o' the plunder, fair and square.
~
The marauders plunder on.
